#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:275
msgid "Human Head"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_heads/init.lua:276
msgid ""
"A human head is a small decorative block which resembles the head of a human "
"(i.e. a player character). It can also be worn as a helmet for fun, but does "
"not offer any protection."
msgstr ""

